1 1. Be duly registered with or under the jurisdiction of the
2 Commission;
3 2. Provide a form of financial security which meets the
4 provisions of Section 160.15 of Title 17 of the Oklahoma Statutes,
5 if applicable, or provide a form of financial security, in the form
6 and amount to be determined by the Commission, as applicable, which
7 shall remain in effect until release is authorized by the
8 Commission; and
9 3. Obtain an approved permit from the Commission.
